descriptionNullable:
This tea sickness dataset contains tea leaves showing 7 common diseases of tea: 

- Red leaf spot
- Algal leaf spot
- Bird’s eyespot;
- Gray blight;
- White spot;
- Anthracnose;
- Brown blight. 

The dataset further contains a class of healthy tea leaves.  Each of the classes contains more than 100 images. The dataset was collected in Johnstone Boiyon farm, Koiwa location, Bomet county from a clone of 1510. It can be used with transfer learning for Machine learning models for predicting sickness in tea.

**Dataset is open-sourced from [here.](https://data.mendeley.com/datasets/j32xdt2ff5/2)**

